## Detailed Permissions

### Student
- View Student Records
- View Course Records
- View Placement Records
- View Attendance Records
- Cannot Create, Edit, or Delete records

### Faculty
- Create and Edit Student Records
- Create and Edit Course Records
- Create and Edit Attendance Records
- View Placement Records

### Placement Officer
- Create and Edit Placement Records
- View Student and Course Records

### HOD
- Manage department-level records
- Review attendance and placement information
- Edit student and course data

### Principal
- View all institutional records
- Monitor overall academic performance

### Salesforce Administrator
- Complete system access
- User management
- Security configuration
- Data management

